## ðŸ§  Tips

- Prepare grains and legumes in batch every Sunday.
- Keep snacks in containers or bags for grab-and-go.
- Freeze cooked meals for variety over the weeks.
- Use FMEL fridge wisely: label items and share space with roommates politely.

